ContentDesc_Aloalo: In a seldom-traveled corner of the south sea isles lies Aloalo, an island filled with lush vegetation and teeming with vibrant wildlife. Yet the survival of this paradise hinges on a delicate natural balance which has only grown more precarious since the island's stewards departed a century ago. Answering the plea of a messenger most peculiar, you must join Matsya on a journey to restore order to Aloalo, and in the process uncover secrets long forgotten.
Instancecontenttextdata_37406_Text: Look, three paths forward. Which one should we take?
Instancecontenttextdata_37407_Text: I see we are of the same mind! Our adventure starts off on the right foot!
Instancecontenttextdata_37408_Text: That way? Really? Well, if you believe it is best!
Instancecontenttextdata_37409_Text: Just past that crest looks like a splendid spot to fish. Let's go, <Split([ObjectParameter(1)], ,1)/>!
Instancecontenttextdata_37410_Text: The ocean carved out these caves over countless years. I suppose we should be grateful the waves are mild at the moment.
Instancecontenttextdata_37411_Text: Is that...a Lalafell!? But Kalika said that the people of this island had fled long ago.
Instancecontenttextdata_37412_Text: Do you smell that, <Split([ObjectParameter(1)], ,1)/>? There's rain coming.
Instancecontenttextdata_37413_Text: Is that...a Lalafell!? But Kalika said that the people of this island had fled long ago.
Instancecontenttextdata_37414_Text: I thought that would be the end of us...but it seems fate has more fishing in store!
Instancecontenttextdata_37415_Text: <Split([ObjectParameter(1)], ,1)/>, a moment? I want to take a look here.
Instancecontenttextdata_37416_Text: Well, if you think so... I'm sure there'll be other spots ahead.
Instancecontenttextdata_37417_Text: Look, it's that Lalafell from before, and he's run afoul of some hungry beasts. We should probably help him, yes?
Instancecontenttextdata_37419_Text: Thank you, <Split([ObjectParameter(1)], ,1)/>! Let's hope for something big!
Instancecontenttextdata_37420_Text: The tide rises with the setting sun. We should watch our step.
Instancecontenttextdata_37422_Text: I want to try different bait. Something suitable must be hiding in these sands─can you help me look?
Instancecontenttextdata_37424_Text: This is perfect! I can feel it─this will lure out something big!
Instancecontenttextdata_37426_Text: This is perfect! I can feel it─this will lure out something big!
Instancecontenttextdata_37427_Text: The fish here are more trouble than they're worth. Let's try somewhere else!
Instancecontenttextdata_37428_Text: I can sense it... A great catch is just ahead!
Instancecontenttextdata_37430_Text: I was frozen in fear...but you had it well in hand, <Split([ObjectParameter(1)], ,1)/>!
Instancecontenttextdata_37431_Text: This is a promising spot. I'd best get my rod ready!
Instancecontenttextdata_37432_Text: May I hook a wonderful gift for Nidhana!
Instancecontenttextdata_37437_Text: This is a promising spot. I'd best get my rod ready!

Instancecontenttextdata_37455_Text: Thavnair's jungles can be dense and difficult to traverse, but this swamp is no less daunting...
Instancecontenttextdata_37456_Text: What strange worms! I doubt they would make for good bait.
Instancecontenttextdata_37458_Text: What's that...? A Miqo'te!? But Kalika said this island was deserted.
Instancecontenttextdata_37459_Text: What's that...? A Miqo'te!? But Kalika said this island was deserted.
Instancecontenttextdata_37460_Text: The path keeps climbing. Could there still be fishing spots above us?
Instancecontenttextdata_37462_Text: People lived here? How did they find the courage to build so high up?
Instancecontenttextdata_37467_Text: You did it! I was worried for a moment, but then I remembered who I was with.
Instancecontenttextdata_37468_Text: Now I can fish at my leisure. What awaits us atop this mighty tree?
Instancecontenttextdata_37474_Text: Now I can fish at my leisure. What awaits us atop this mighty tree?
Instancecontenttextdata_37479_Text: It appears the only way forward is down...
Instancecontenttextdata_37481_Text: Now I can fish at my leisure. What awaits us atop this mighty tree?
Instancecontenttextdata_37488_Text: Now I can fish at my leisure. What awaits us atop this mighty tree?
Instancecontenttextdata_37493_Text: People once lived here. And people build near the best fishing spots!
Instancecontenttextdata_37494_Text: I can barely make out my own hands.
Instancecontenttextdata_37495_Text: I see a great spot to fish just ahead. Let's go, <Split([ObjectParameter(1)], ,1)/>!
Instancecontenttextdata_37497_Text: Phew... Now we can move forward. I know good fishing awaits!
Instancecontenttextdata_37498_Text: We've climbed quite a ways. I wonder if there are fish to be found up here?
Instancecontenttextdata_37499_Text: You there! If it's treasure you seek, I can help!
Instancecontenttextdata_37500_Text: Yes, yes, I know where great riches are kept. I can guide you there with a snap of my fingers!
Instancecontenttextdata_37501_Text: Are we even on the same island? And where did that faerie go?
Instancecontenttextdata_37502_Text: You've made it! As for the treasure you seek─it's right over there!
Instancecontenttextdata_37503_Text: Hahaha! You fell for it! Fools!
Instancecontenttextdata_37506_Text: And there I thought you'd be fun. Fine! May the sun bleach your bones!
Instancecontenttextdata_37507_Text: I think we made her mad... Wait, how do we get out of here?
Instancecontenttextdata_37508_Text: Here! A bit overgrown, but I can clear the way. <Split([ObjectParameter(1)], ,1)/>, stay on my heels!
Instancecontenttextdata_37509_Text: Look, more statues. It's almost as if they've been waiting for someone...
Instancecontenttextdata_37510_Text: A lever to open a door, it would seem. We can continue onward.
Instancecontenttextdata_37511_Text: <shiver> A bit chilly, don't you think? Too cold for people to have lived here, perhaps.
Instancecontenttextdata_37512_Text: The path opened! Your prayers were heard!
Instancecontenttextdata_37518_Text: Let that be a lesson in proper manners! I can hear water coming from deeper inside─let's go, <Split([ObjectParameter(1)], ,1)/>!
Instancecontenttextdata_37519_Text: Just as I had hoped─a fishing spot! May it yield a catch that will bring a smile to Nidhana's face!
Instancecontenttextdata_37520_Text: He's the one who summoned that wooden monstrosity! What is it now?
Instancecontenttextdata_37525_Text: Let that be a lesson in proper manners! I can hear water coming from deeper inside─let's go!
Instancecontenttextdata_37526_Text: Just as I had hoped─a fishing spot! May it yield a catch that will bring a smile to Nidhana's face!
Instancecontenttextdata_37528_Text: This fishing spot is almost worth the trouble that faerie caused. Almost...
Instancecontenttextdata_37533_Text: Let that be a lesson in proper manners! I can hear water coming from deeper inside─let's go!
Instancecontenttextdata_37534_Text: Just as I had hoped─a fishing spot! May it yield a catch that will bring a smile to Nidhana's face!
Instancecontenttextdata_37543_Text: Any fishing spots this close to the jewel must be teeming with rare fish!
Instancecontenttextdata_37549_Text: Intruders detected. Initializing computational engine... Calculating optimal tactics.
Instancecontenttextdata_37550_Text: Calculations complete. Deploying arcane measures to eliminate intruders.
Instancecontenttextdata_37551_Text: Recalculating optimal tactics... Commencing terrestrial assault.
Instancecontenttextdata_37552_Text: Threat assessment complete. Probable weaknesses determined.
Instancecontenttextdata_37555_Text: Gods, that smarts! Seems I'm in over my head, so...good luck!
Instancecontenttextdata_37556_Text: It flies! Like something out of a children's tale!
Instancecontenttextdata_37557_Text: Remember me? I ain't the kind of scoundrel what shirks his debts, so I'll help you out─just this once.
Instancecontenttextdata_37558_Text: Now we're even! So if you'll excuse me, I've got a treasure to plunder!
Instancecontenttextdata_37559_Text: You in the habit of leavin' people for dead!? I'll make you wish those beasts finished me off!
Instancecontenttextdata_37560_Text: Bloody─! Better escape while I still have my head!
Instancecontenttextdata_37561_Text: Plenty of wind and water...just what I need to call my minions!
Instancecontenttextdata_37562_Text: These are even nastier than the last! Don't let them take a bite out of you!
Instancecontenttextdata_37564_Text: You're here too!? Then I must be on the right track!
Instancecontenttextdata_37565_Text: If it's all the same to you, I'll go on ahead. Mind keepin' my pet company in the meantime?
Instancecontenttextdata_37566_Text: If you went down this path, that means the treasure's at the end of it!
Instancecontenttextdata_37567_Text: Know if this thing eats? Well, you'll find out soon enough! That jewel is ours!
Instancecontenttextdata_37568_Text: J-Just let us have the treasure, and no one needs to get hurt!
Instancecontenttextdata_37569_Text: If you insist on staying the course, you'll have to deal with Quaqua. I can't guarantee your safety!
Instancecontenttextdata_37570_Text: This beast is made from wood! Where did they find it!?
Instancecontenttextdata_37571_Text: It conjured weapons from thin air!
Instancecontenttextdata_37572_Text: More weapons! Those hammers look heavy enough to shatter stone!
Instancecontenttextdata_37573_Text: It called monsters to its aid! Don't let them catch you!
Instancecontenttextdata_37574_Text: Be careful! The flames move like waves!
Instancecontenttextdata_37575_Text: So many of them! Where will you run to!?
Instancecontenttextdata_37576_Text: Its arsenal is endless! Sisters protect me from those blades!
Instancecontenttextdata_37578_Text: Spears of water!? Oh gods, here they come!
Instancecontenttextdata_37579_Text: The water is spilling forth! Can you manage, <Split([ObjectParameter(1)], ,1)/>?
Instancecontenttextdata_37580_Text: It's using the fetid water as a weapon!
Instancecontenttextdata_37581_Text: Watch out! You don't want dirty water in your boots!
Instancecontenttextdata_37583_Text: Huh!? The statues are emitting light!
Instancecontenttextdata_37584_Text: What!? The light swallowed the orbs!
Instancecontenttextdata_37585_Text: The statues must house ancient power. I'm glad they're on our side.
Instancecontenttextdata_37587_Text: We made it. None of its weapons could match yours, <Split([ObjectParameter(1)], ,1)/>.
Instancecontenttextdata_37589_Text: You saw right through her tricks! Well done!
Instancecontenttextdata_37590_Text: More treasure chests...don't pick the wrong one!
Instancecontenttextdata_37591_Text: Something tells me these toys aren't meant for children...
Instancecontenttextdata_37592_Text: I saw it! Watch your step, <Split([ObjectParameter(1)], ,1)/>!
Instancecontenttextdata_37593_Text: This looks like a good spot to fish. Can we stop for a moment?
Instancecontenttextdata_37594_Text: It's back where it was, like it never tried to murder us. Let's hope it stays that way...
Instancecontenttextdata_37601_Text: Hahaha! I knew you'd walk into my trap!
Instancecontenttextdata_37602_Text: Not that way! Step there! There!
Instancecontenttextdata_37603_Text: I'm graceful in all things, especially reloading!
Instancecontenttextdata_37605_Text: This is fun! So fun that I'll do it again!
Instancecontenttextdata_37606_Text: This is what you were looking for, right? Treasure! But which one is the real thing?
Instancecontenttextdata_37609_Text: Gather round, one and all! I've prepared a special gift for this very special day!
Instancecontenttextdata_37610_Text: How did you like them? Find one that tickles your fancy?
Instancecontenttextdata_37611_Text: Hahaha! I just love that sound!
Instancecontenttextdata_37613_Text: Now for the main event: darts! Hope you've been practicing!
Instancecontenttextdata_37615_Text: Hehehe... Round and round it goes─but where it stops, nobody knows!
Instancecontenttextdata_37616_Text: Ahaha! A meteor upon your heads!
Instancecontenttextdata_37617_Text: Your prize is...a giant hammer to the noggin!
Instancecontenttextdata_37618_Text: Too bad! But don't despair─even losers get a prize!
Instancecontenttextdata_37619_Text: Congratulations! You've been blessed by luck─now be blessed by me!
Instancecontenttextdata_37620_Text: Waaahhh! I give up! I'm sorry, I'm sorry! I just wanted to have a little fun...
Instancecontenttextdata_37634_Text: These ships all ran aground... Not even Thavnair's stormy shores have claimed so many.
Instancecontenttextdata_37642_Text: Wh-Why would the statue attack us!? Perhaps we're not supposed to be here...
Instancecontenttextdata_37643_Text: The birds are growing bigger and bigger! Is this the jewel's doing?
Instancecontenttextdata_37644_Text: Just look at me! How could you deny such an innocent face?
Instancecontenttextdata_37645_Text: Lost, are we? It's all right, I know the way. Trust in me and I'll guide you true!
Instancecontenttextdata_37647_Text: Revising threat assessment... Integrating additional tactics into stratagem.
Instancecontenttextdata_37649_Text: It really is impressive, but I'd rather not wait around for it to try and squash us again.
Instancecontenttextdata_37650_Text: I knew following you was the right move. Apologies, but I'm afraid the treasure is ours!
Instancecontenttextdata_37651_Text: Huh? What happened to the mist?
Instancecontenttextdata_37652_Text: Ah, the cushion broke your fall! How oddly considerate of her...
Instancecontenttextdata_37654_Text: Oh my... The statue is carved into the tree itself! Could it be the Speaker Kalika serves!?
Instancecontenttextdata_37655_Text: Show me what you're made of!
Instancecontenttextdata_37656_Text: Water's in the air, and I'll bend it to my will!
Instancecontenttextdata_37657_Text: Show me what you're made of!
Instancecontenttextdata_37658_Text: In any other situation, these crystals would be enchanting.
Instancecontenttextdata_37659_Text: That crystal is different from the others. I'd keep a wide berth if I were you!
Instancecontenttextdata_37660_Text: A bubble seems to be holding one crystal aloft. We should keep an eye on that...
Instancecontenttextdata_37661_Text: The bubbles make the crystals light as air. A single gust of wind will send them flying!
Instancecontenttextdata_37662_Text: There he is again! He said he'd help us, but can we trust him?
Instancecontenttextdata_37664_Text: There he is again! He doesn't look happy to see us...
Instancecontenttextdata_37666_Text: Watch out! The wind howls again!
Instancecontenttextdata_37669_Text: Are we the intruders!? What could we be intruding upon?
Instancecontenttextdata_37671_Text: The direction of its magicks don't match the patterns. What puzzle is it putting before us?
Npcyell_16090_Text: If it were up to me...
Npcyell_16093_Text: I don't think my fishing hook will be of use here!
Npcyell_16094_Text: I'd rather not do that again...
Npcyell_16095_Text: Get too close and you'll be in for a shock!
Npcyell_16096_Text: Do you think some monsters prefer rainy days over sunny days?
Npcyell_16097_Text: Those claws will cut us in two!
Npcyell_16098_Text: A crab that big could feed a whole village...
Npcyell_16106_Text: You just going to stand there!? Cold-blooded bastards!
Npcyell_16107_Text: Maybe he shouldn't have set that beast upon us...
Npcyell_16110_Text: Not even a word of thanks.
Npcyell_16112_Text: Fish are close, I know it!
Npcyell_16113_Text: To the patient go the fish!
Npcyell_16114_Text: Oh, what's this? Such a strong bite!
Npcyell_16115_Text: To the patient go the fish!
Npcyell_16116_Text: Oh, what's this? Such a strong bite!
Npcyell_16123_Text: Those things sent a chill down my spine.
Npcyell_16124_Text: A toad that big could swallow us whole!
Npcyell_16125_Text: I'm glad we didn't end up as its dinner...
Npcyell_16127_Text: I was afraid you'd be eaten alive!
Npcyell_16128_Text: Ugh... The hairs on my skin are standing on end.
Npcyell_16131_Text: What other surprises does this island have in store?
Npcyell_16132_Text: What a majestic bird...but that beak looks sharp as a sword!
Npcyell_16134_Text: I've never seen a bat so large!
Npcyell_16135_Text: The bats in Thavnair are not nearly as big...or ferocious.
Npcyell_16137_Text: Uwah! How did you─ Leave me alone!
Npcyell_16138_Text: Finally, statues that stay where they are.
Npcyell_16139_Text: May thoughts of Nidhana give me courage!
Npcyell_16144_Text: May thoughts of Nidhana give me courage!
Npcyell_16145_Text: <heavy breathing> I think that shaved a few summers off my life.
Npcyell_16149_Text: I've had my fill of wild animals already...
Npcyell_16151_Text: I didn't know coconuts could grow to such sizes.
Npcyell_16152_Text: Look, an asvattha! Just as horrifying here as they are in Thavnair.
Npcyell_16153_Text: No, even more horrifying...the asvattha here smell much worse.
Npcyell_16157_Text: My legs don't want to move forward, but I must.
Npcyell_16158_Text: We've walked into a lizard den!
Npcyell_16159_Text: We can go further in from here.
Npcyell_16162_Text: This is no way to treat visitors!
Npcyell_16165_Text: Look at the size of that thing!
Npcyell_16166_Text: There has to be a path somewhere...
Npcyell_16168_Text: How deep does this path go?
Npcyell_16169_Text: Treasure chests? In a place like this?
Npcyell_16171_Text: We can't go any further. We'll have to find another way.
Npcyell_16177_Text: The mist is so thick I can barely see my own trunk...
Npcyell_16178_Text: The mist is so thick I can barely see my own trunk...
Npcyell_16228_Text: A Roegadyn? I thought this island was deserted?
Npcyell_16230_Text: I need...I need a moment to catch my breath.
Npcyell_16252_Text: Have you ever beheld such grace as mine!?
Npcyell_16253_Text: Phew...I'm going through a lot of bullets.
Npcyell_16258_Text: You'll never guess what I've got in store...
Npcyell_16262_Text: This scenery reminds me of home...
Npcyell_16263_Text: Gaaah! I'm not afraid, I'm not afraid...
Npcyell_16265_Text: This looks like a great spot to cast my rod.
Npcyell_16266_Text: Hmm... Not a single fish I haven't seen before.
Npcyell_16270_Text: What was in the chests, I wonder?
Npcyell_16372_Text: Does every beast on this island want to kill us?
Npcyell_16373_Text: I admit...that was scary, but exciting.
Npcyell_16448_Text: Oh, you ruined it! I'd packed the chests full of goodies, too!
Npcyell_16449_Text: You aren't going to jump...are you?
Npcyell_16450_Text: I can do this! I can!
Npcyell_16451_Text: Every twist and turn brings us face-to-face with a new threat...
Npcyell_16453_Text: Do you think she's telling the truth, <Split([ObjectParameter(1)], ,1)/>?
Npcyell_16456_Text: The slightest touch should be enough to clear it...
Npcyell_16457_Text: The wind made it brittle for us. Now we can pass through!
Npcyell_16459_Text: Let's hope the divinities of Aloalo guide us true.
Npcyell_16460_Text: Nothing for it but to keep going!
Npcyell_16461_Text: We made it through the mist!
Npcyell_16463_Text: Didn't expect that. Well, no point in sticking around!
Npcyell_16465_Text: I almost fainted... Where are we?
Npcyell_16466_Text: Everywhere we go, beasts are waiting for us!
Npcyell_16469_Text: Hehe. Now this could be interesting.
Npcyell_16470_Text: I won't say no to treasure, but what I'm really here for is the fish!
Npcyell_16522_Text: I can't take any more of his pestering.
Npcyell_16523_Text: How could something so large move so quickly!?
Npcyell_16526_Text: I try to only speak kindly of others, but they test me...
Npcyell_16527_Text: I try to only speak kindly of others, but they test me...
